Paloma...

1162
01:27:53,247 --> 01:27:54,503
Steckelhörn 3!

1163
01:28:20,352 --> 01:28:21,937
What's the matter, Hannes?

1164
01:28:22,057 --> 01:28:24,567
Nothing... nothing at all...

1165
01:28:25,495 --> 01:28:29,111
I was just dreaming...

1166
01:28:30,972 --> 01:28:33,355
Go back to sleep, Gisa!

1167
